OL,3,CTransport minister calls P&O Ferries
OL,4,C'rogue operator' as law is tightened
OL,6,FThe transport secretary has told ITV
OL,7,FNews she believes P&O Ferries is a
OL,8,F"rogue operator" - revealing she has
OL,9,Fbeen boycotting them for years. ITV
OL,10,FNews Business Editor Joel Hills
OL,11,Freports from Dover
OL,13,FAt Port of Dover, P&O Pioneer prepares
OL,14,Fto set sail for France.
OL,16,FTwo and a half years ago, P&O caused
OL,17,Fcontroversy by sacking almost 800
OL,18,FBritish seafarers without warning and
OL,19,Freplacing them with cheaper, foreign
OL,20,Fagency crew.
