OL,6,FIn opposition, Labour was outraged. In
OL,7,Fgovernment, they are taking action.
OL,9,F"In less than 100 days of this
OL,10,Fgovernment, we have brought forward
OL,11,Flegislation that will mean P&O Ferries
OL,12,Fand the scandal that it brought to
OL,13,FBritain will never happen again,"
OL,14,FTransport Secretary Louise Haigh told
OL,15,FITV News.
