OL,4,C'rogue operator' as law is tightened
OL,6,FFrom December 1, ferry operators that
OL,7,Fregularly call at UK ports at least
OL,8,F120 times a year will have to pay
OL,9,Ftheir seafarers at least the
OL,10,Fequivalent of the UK National Minimum
OL,11,FWage.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,FThey will legally have to inform the
OL,19,Fgovernment of any plans to dismiss
OL,20,Fmore than 20 employees.
