OL,6,FAnd the new Employment Rights Bill
OL,7,Fincludes a measure to end so-called
OL,8,F"fire and rehire" practices "except
OL,9,Fwhere employers genuinely have no
OL,10,Falternative".
OL,12,FThat may sound a little like a
OL,13,Floophole to you. It does to Darren
OL,14,FProctor, National Secretary of the RMT
OL,15,FUnion.
