OL,6,F"This is a step in the right
OL,7,Fdirection," Proctor says. "But there
OL,8,Fis a lot of wiggle room. And it's
OL,9,Fsomething we need to strengthen going
OL,10,Fforward because what shipping industry
OL,11,Fhas always done is look for wriggle
OL,12,Froom, they've manoeuvred around
OL,13,Flegation, they've looked for
OL,14,Floopholes."
OL,16,FThe law in Britain is set to change to
OL,17,Fimprove pay and working conditions for
OL,18,Fseafarers but the French government
OL,19,Fhas acted sooner and gone further.
