OL,3,CTransport minister calls P&O Ferries
OL,4,C'rogue operator' as law is tightened
OL,6,FSince June, French law compels P&O
OL,7,FFerries to pay the salaire minimum de
OL,8,Fcroissance (minimum wage) and limited
OL,9,Fthe hours the company can ask crew to
OL,10,Fwork.
OL,12,FITV News has learned that P&O has
OL,13,Fresponded by laying off many of the
OL,14,Fforeign agency workers it hired to
OL,15,Freplace the British crew it fired two
OL,16,Fyears ago.
OL,18,FP&O Ferries was employing several
OL,19,Fhundred people from as far afield as
OL,20,FIndia, the Philippines and Indonesia.
