OL,6,FSome were paid as little as #5 an hour
OL,7,Fand asked to work for up 17 weeks
OL,8,Fwithout a day off.
OL,10,FITV News understands that P&O has let
OL,11,Fmany of them go, including one crew
OL,12,Fmember who was recently given an award
OL,13,Ffor his "commitment and dedication to
OL,14,Fthe company".
OL,16,F"I feel really sorry for these foreign
OL,17,Fworkers," says John Lansdown, one of
OL,18,Fthe seafarers P&O dismissed in March
OL,19,F2022.
