OL,6,F"We were sacked because we were 'too
OL,7,Fexpensive' and now it appears that
OL,8,Fthese foreign workers are being
OL,9,Freplaced by P&O Ferries because they
OL,10,Fare too costly to fly in. That is
OL,11,Fabsolutely appalling".
OL,13,FThe new transport secretary is
OL,14,Funimpressed with P&O's behaviour.
