OL,3,CTransport minister calls P&O Ferries
OL,4,C'rogue operator' as law is tightened
OL,6,F"They're a rogue operator. We're
OL,7,Fcracking down on the way that they
OL,8,Ftreated employees, and we want to see
OL,9,Fthem mirror the standards of other
OL,10,Foperators that come in and out of
OL,11,FGreat Britain's waters," she told ITV
OL,12,FNews.
OL,14,FAsked if she would travel with P&O
OL,15,FFerries, she replied: "No, I've been
OL,16,Fboycotting P&O Ferries for two and a
OL,17,Fhalf years, and I encourage consumers
OL,18,Fto do the same."
