OL,6,FA spokesperson for P&O Ferries said:
OL,7,F"The UK and French Governments have
OL,8,Fbrought forward legislation with far
OL,9,Freaching impacts on the labour market
OL,10,Ffor seafarers on cross channel ferry
OL,11,Fservices. P&O Ferries always complies
OL,12,Fwith all relevant national and
OL,13,Finternational laws, and as such we
OL,14,Fhave made changes to our crewing
OL,15,Fpolicies to meet new legal
OL,16,Frequirements."
