OL,6,FThe company says the French
OL,7,Fgovernment's decision to limit crew
OL,8,Frotations to 2 weeks onboard ship and
OL,9,F2 weeks rest "means it is no longer
OL,10,Fpractical to employ crew from outside
OL,11,FEurope in large numbers, due to travel
OL,12,Ftime and the requirements of the
OL,13,Fimmigration system.
OL,15,FThe statement added: "P&O Ferries is
OL,16,Fcommitted to operating the highest
OL,17,Fstandards of service and we continue
OL,18,Fto recruit qualified and highly
OL,19,Fexperienced international seafarers.
